# PR review bot replies

Bot reply standard is defined inline in `git-pr-workflow-default.mdc` (section "Bot/reviewer reply standard").

**Summary:** for every substantive thread from `gemini-code-assist`, `chatgpt-codex-connector`, `copilot`, `coderabbit`, `sourcery-ai`, scanners — reply in-thread before merge: implemented (+ SHA) / deferred (reason) / declined (reason). Do not merge with unanswered threads. Green `ci_result` does not replace thread closure.
